---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="IoT Sensor Visualization Lab"
  description="Digital twin demo with synthetic IoT sensor data, heatmap overlays, and time-series playback on the RAPS WASM viewer."
>
  <div class="tool-container">
    <h1 class="tool-title">IoT Sensor Visualization Lab</h1>
    <p class="tool-subtitle">
      Load a 3D model, activate synthetic IoT sensors, toggle surface heatmaps, and scrub through a 24-hour simulated workday. No backend, no real sensors — all data generated in the browser.
    </p>

    <div class="raps-tip">
      <h3>How it works</h3>
      <p>
        The <strong>extension API</strong> lets plugins hook into the viewer lifecycle. The <strong>IoT extension</strong> is the first plugin — it manages sensor sprites, surface heatmaps, and tooltips. The <strong>synthetic connector</strong> generates deterministic time-series data (temperature, CO2, humidity, occupancy) so the demo works without any infrastructure.
      </p>
      <p>Swap the connector for a <code>WebSocketConnector</code> or <code>MqttConnector</code> to use real sensor data.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="page-grid">
      <section class="stage-card">
        <div class="toolbar">
          <div class="toolbar-group">
            <button id="load-obj-btn" class="tool-btn primary">Load OBJ sample</button>
            <button id="load-ifc-btn" class="tool-btn secondary">Load IFC sample</button>
            <button id="load-building-btn" class="tool-btn warning">Load building</button>
            <label class="upload-btn" for="file-input">
              <span>Upload model</span>
              <input type="file" id="file-input" accept=".obj,.stl,.ifc" />
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class="toolbar-group">
            <button id="iot-btn" class="tool-btn ghost">IoT Sensors</button>
            <button id="heatmap-btn" class="tool-btn ghost" disabled>Heatmap</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="status-bar">
          <div>
            <div class="status-label">Status</div>
            <div id="status-text" class="status-value">Load a model to get started...</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="status-label">Sensors</div>
            <div id="sensor-text" class="status-value muted">No sensors active</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="viewer-shell">
          <raps-viewer id="viewer" background="#0b1120"></raps-viewer>
        </div>

        <div class="time-strip">
          <button id="play-btn" class="tool-btn ghost" disabled>Play</button>
          <div class="time-slider-wrap">
            <input type="range" id="timeline" min="0" max="86400000" value="43200000" step="60000" disabled />
          </div>
          <span id="time-label" class="time-display">12:00</span>
          <div class="speed-group">
            <button id="speed-1x" class="speed-btn active" disabled>1x</button>
            <button id="speed-10x" class="speed-btn" disabled>10x</button>
            <button id="speed-60x" class="speed-btn" disabled>60x</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <aside class="info-card">
        <h2>Sensor Dashboard</h2>
        <p class="muted-text">Activate IoT sensors to see live readings.</p>

        <div id="sensor-grid" class="sensor-grid">
          <div class="empty-state">Load a model and click "IoT Sensors" to begin.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="notes-card">
          <h3>Sensor types</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Temperature</strong> — diurnal sine cycle peaking at 14:00, with zone offsets and noise.</li>
            <li><strong>CO2</strong> — correlated with occupancy, ramps during work hours, ventilation decay after 18:00.</li>
            <li><strong>Humidity</strong> — slow drift with periodic HVAC correction cycles.</li>
            <li><strong>Occupancy</strong> — sigmoid arrival/departure curves around business hours.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="notes-card">
          <h3>Architecture</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Extension API</strong> — <code>loadExtension()</code> / <code>unloadExtension()</code> with <code>onFrame</code> dispatch.</li>
            <li><strong>Connector interface</strong> — <code>SensorConnector</code> abstracts data sources. Swap <code>SyntheticConnector</code> for real backends.</li>
            <li><strong>Sprite layer</strong> — single <code>THREE.Points</code> draw call, vertex colors, zero-allocation updates.</li>
            <li><strong>Heatmap shader</strong> — GLSL inverse-distance weighting, up to 64 sensors via uniforms.</li>
            <li><strong>Tooltip</strong> — DOM overlay with <code>Float64Array</code> ring buffer sparkline.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="importmap" is:inline>
    {
      "imports": {
        "three": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.170.0/build/three.module.js"
      }
    }
  </script>

  <script type="module" is:inline>
    import {
      IoTExtension,
      SyntheticConnector,
    } from '/vendor/raps-viewer.js';
    import {
      buildBuildingModel,
    } from '/tools/viewer-generators.js';

    const viewer = document.getElementById('viewer');
    const fileInput = document.getElementById('file-input');
    const statusText = document.getElementById('status-text');
    const sensorText = document.getElementById('sensor-text');
    const iotBtn = document.getElementById('iot-btn');
    const heatmapBtn = document.getElementById('heatmap-btn');
    const playBtn = document.getElementById('play-btn');
    const timeline = document.getElementById('timeline');
    const timeLabel = document.getElementById('time-label');
    const sensorGrid = document.getElementById('sensor-grid');
    const speedButtons = [
      document.getElementById('speed-1x'),
      document.getElementById('speed-10x'),
      document.getElementById('speed-60x'),
    ];

    let iotExt = null;
    let connector = null;
    let heatmapActive = false;
    let currentSpeed = 60;

    const defaultSensors = [
      { id: 'temp-nw', type: 'temperature', position: [-0.4, 0.5, -0.4], unit: '\u00b0C', range: [15, 35] },
      { id: 'temp-ne', type: 'temperature', position: [0.4, 0.5, -0.4], unit: '\u00b0C', range: [15, 35] },
      { id: 'temp-sw', type: 'temperature', position: [-0.4, 0.5, 0.4], unit: '\u00b0C', range: [15, 35] },
      { id: 'temp-se', type: 'temperature', position: [0.4, 0.5, 0.4], unit: '\u00b0C', range: [15, 35] },
      { id: 'co2-center', type: 'co2', position: [0, 0.5, 0], unit: 'ppm', range: [400, 2000] },
      { id: 'humidity-1', type: 'humidity', position: [0, 1.5, 0], unit: '%', range: [30, 80] },
    ];

    function nextFrame() {
      return new Promise((resolve) => requestAnimationFrame(() => resolve()));
    }

    async function ensureViewerReady() {
      await customElements.whenDefined('raps-viewer');
      await nextFrame();
      await nextFrame();
    }

    function setIoTControls(enabled) {
      heatmapBtn.disabled = !enabled;
      playBtn.disabled = !enabled;
      timeline.disabled = !enabled;
      speedButtons.forEach((b) => (b.disabled = !enabled));
    }

    function formatTime(ms) {
      const hours = Math.floor((ms / 3_600_000) % 24);
      const mins = Math.floor((ms / 60_000) % 60);
      return `${String(hours).padStart(2, '0')}:${String(mins).padStart(2, '0')}`;
    }

    function renderSensorCards(sensors) {
      sensorGrid.innerHTML = '';
      for (const s of sensors) {
        const card = document.createElement('div');
        card.className = 'sensor-card';
        card.id = `sensor-card-${s.id}`;
        card.innerHTML = `
          <div class="sensor-id">${s.id}</div>
          <div class="sensor-type">${s.type}</div>
          <div class="sensor-value" id="sval-${s.id}">--</div>
          <div class="sensor-unit">${s.unit}</div>
        `;
        sensorGrid.appendChild(card);
      }
    }

    function updateSensorCards() {
      if (!iotExt || !connector) return;
      for (const s of defaultSensors) {
        const val = iotExt.getSensorValue(s.id);
        const el = document.getElementById(`sval-${s.id}`);
        if (el && val !== null) {
          el.textContent = val.toFixed(1);
        }
      }
    }

    // --- Model loading ---

    async function loadSource(source, label) {
      statusText.textContent = label;
      try {
        await ensureViewerReady();
        await viewer.load(source);
        statusText.textContent = 'Model loaded';
      } catch (error) {
        statusText.textContent = `Load failed: ${error.message}`;
      }
    }

    document.getElementById('load-obj-btn').addEventListener('click', () => {
      loadSource('/tools/viewer-fixtures/demo-pyramid.obj', 'Loading OBJ sample...');
    });

    document.getElementById('load-ifc-btn').addEventListener('click', () => {
      loadSource('/tools/viewer-fixtures/demo-box.ifc', 'Loading IFC sample...');
    });

    document.getElementById('load-building-btn').addEventListener('click', async () => {
      statusText.textContent = 'Generating building...';
      try {
        await ensureViewerReady();
        await new Promise((r) => setTimeout(r, 0));
        const model = buildBuildingModel();
        const file = new File([model.obj], `${model.name}.obj`, { type: 'text/plain' });
        await viewer.load(file);
        statusText.textContent = `Loaded: ${model.metadata.summary}`;
      } catch (error) {
        statusText.textContent = `Load failed: ${error.message}`;
      }
    });

    fileInput.addEventListener('change', () => {
      const file = fileInput.files?.[0];
      if (!file) return;
      loadSource(file, `Loading ${file.name}...`);
    });

    viewer.addEventListener('progress', (e) => {
      statusText.textContent = `Loading: ${e.detail.phase}...`;
    });

    viewer.addEventListener('select', (e) => {
      const suffix = e.detail.entityType ? ` (${e.detail.entityType})` : '';
      statusText.textContent = `Selected entity ${e.detail.entityId}${suffix}`;
    });

    // --- IoT controls ---

    iotBtn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
      await ensureViewerReady();

      if (iotExt) {
        // Deactivate
        connector.pause();
        viewer.unloadExtension('iot');
        iotExt = null;
        connector = null;
        heatmapActive = false;
        iotBtn.classList.remove('active');
        heatmapBtn.classList.remove('active');
        playBtn.classList.remove('active');
        playBtn.textContent = 'Play';
        setIoTControls(false);
        sensorText.textContent = 'No sensors active';
        sensorGrid.innerHTML = '<div class="empty-state">Sensors deactivated.</div>';
        return;
      }

      // Activate
      connector = new SyntheticConnector({
        sensors: defaultSensors,
        intervalMs: 500,
        timeScale: currentSpeed,
      });
      connector.seek(43200000); // noon

      iotExt = new IoTExtension(connector);
      viewer.loadExtension(iotExt);
      connector.play();

      iotBtn.classList.add('active');
      playBtn.classList.add('active');
      playBtn.textContent = 'Pause';
      setIoTControls(true);
      sensorText.textContent = `${defaultSensors.length} sensors active`;

      renderSensorCards(defaultSensors);
    });

    heatmapBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (!iotExt) return;
      heatmapActive = !heatmapActive;
      iotExt.showHeatmap(heatmapActive);
      heatmapBtn.classList.toggle('active', heatmapActive);
    });

    playBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (!connector) return;
      if (connector.isPlaying) {
        connector.pause();
        playBtn.classList.remove('active');
        playBtn.textContent = 'Play';
      } else {
        connector.play();
        playBtn.classList.add('active');
        playBtn.textContent = 'Pause';
      }
    });

    timeline.addEventListener('input', () => {
      if (!connector) return;
      connector.seek(Number(timeline.value));
    });

    speedButtons.forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const speed = parseInt(btn.textContent, 10);
        currentSpeed = speed;
        speedButtons.forEach((b) => b.classList.remove('active'));
        btn.classList.add('active');
        if (connector && connector.isPlaying) {
          connector.pause();
          connector.play(speed);
        }
      });
    });

    // --- Animation loop for UI updates ---

    function tick() {
      if (connector) {
        const ms = connector.currentTime;
        timeLabel.textContent = formatTime(ms);
        timeline.value = String(ms % 86_400_000);
        updateSensorCards();
      }
      requestAnimationFrame(tick);
    }
    tick();

    // Auto-load default model
    loadSource('/tools/viewer-fixtures/demo-pyramid.obj', 'Loading default OBJ sample...');
  </script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .tool-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .tool-title {
    @apply text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4 text-center;
  }

  .tool-subtitle {
    @apply text-center text-slate-300 mb-8 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto;
  }

  .raps-tip {
    @apply bg-blue-950/30 border border-blue-800/30 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8;
  }

  .raps-tip h3 {
    @apply text-lg font-semibold text-blue-300 mb-3 mt-0;
  }

  .raps-tip p {
    @apply text-slate-300 mb-3 last:mb-0;
  }

  .raps-tip code {
    @apply bg-blue-900/50 text-blue-200 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm font-mono;
  }

  .page-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.8fr) minmax(320px, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .stage-card,
  .info-card {
    @apply bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6;
  }

  .info-card h2 {
    @apply text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1 mt-0;
  }

  .muted-text {
    @apply text-sm text-slate-400 mb-4;
  }

  .toolbar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .toolbar-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .tool-btn,
  .upload-btn {
    @apply inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors cursor-pointer;
  }

  .tool-btn.primary {
    @apply bg-rapeseed-500 text-slate-900 hover:bg-rapeseed-400;
  }

  .tool-btn.secondary {
    @apply bg-cyan-600 text-white hover:bg-cyan-500;
  }

  .tool-btn.warning {
    @apply bg-amber-500 text-slate-950 hover:bg-amber-400;
  }

  .tool-btn.ghost,
  .upload-btn {
    @apply bg-slate-800 text-slate-200 border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-500 hover:text-white;
  }

  .tool-btn.active {
    @apply bg-emerald-600 text-white border-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-500;
  }

  .tool-btn:disabled,
  .upload-btn:has(input:disabled) {
    @apply opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed;
  }

  .upload-btn input {
    display: none;
  }

  .status-bar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .status-label {
    @apply text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500 mb-1;
  }

  .status-value {
    @apply text-sm font-medium text-white;
  }

  .status-value.muted {
    @apply text-slate-400;
  }

  .viewer-shell {
    @apply rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 overflow-hidden bg-slate-950;
    min-height: 520px;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.05);
  }

  .viewer-shell raps-viewer {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 520px;
  }

  .time-strip {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    @apply bg-slate-950/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4;
  }

  .time-slider-wrap {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .time-slider-wrap input[type="range"] {
    width: 100%;
    accent-color: #10b981;
  }

  .time-display {
    @apply text-lg font-mono font-semibold text-emerald-400;
    min-width: 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .speed-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .speed-btn {
    @apply rounded px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold bg-slate-800 text-slate-400 border border-slate-700 cursor-pointer transition-colors;
  }

  .speed-btn.active {
    @apply bg-emerald-600 text-white border-emerald-500;
  }

  .speed-btn:disabled {
    @apply opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed;
  }

  .sensor-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .sensor-card {
    @apply rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/60 p-4;
  }

  .sensor-id {
    @apply text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 mb-1;
  }

  .sensor-type {
    @apply text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-400 mb-2;
  }

  .sensor-value {
    @apply text-2xl font-semibold text-white;
  }

  .sensor-unit {
    @apply text-xs text-slate-500;
  }

  .empty-state {
    @apply text-sm text-slate-500 col-span-2 text-center py-8;
  }

  .notes-card {
    @apply rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/60 p-4 mb-4;
  }

  .notes-card h3 {
    @apply text-base font-semibold text-white mt-0 mb-3;
  }

  .notes-card ul {
    @apply text-sm text-slate-300 pl-5 m-0 space-y-2;
  }

  .notes-card code {
    @apply bg-slate-900/80 text-emerald-300 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .page-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .status-bar {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sensor-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .viewer-shell,
    .viewer-shell raps-viewer {
      min-height: 400px;
      height: 400px;
    }

    .time-strip {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  }
</style>
